data.title: Ethereum Price Falls Under $3,000, But Experts Say Supercycle Is Just ‘Starting’
data.description: The cryptocurrency market has slipped into the red zone. Bitcoin has once again dipped below the $90k mark and Ethereum has crashed to $2800. Amid this tense situation, Sharplink CEO Joseph Chalom has opened up about a possible Ethereum supercycle. In an interview with Milkroad, he said that a few…
